description:
Darkness Radio presents Supernatural News/Parashare: The Creature Feature Edition with Beer City Bruiser!! 

It has been a hot and sticky week world wide and it is bringing out the paranormal, Tim and Bruiser have jumped out of the pool and dried off enough to get the news together and ready for you!

This week,  Aliens come out to watch England burn up in the summer heat! Ghosts are pushing your beer over in pubs! A man kills his friend because he thinks he is going to feed him to Bigfoot! A Redditor who claims they worked for NASA says they found the end of our world with the James Webb Telescope! AND... Bruiser finds his Spirit Animal!!!
